      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Prerequisites</strong> ghost pony</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">So long have you gazed into infinity, nothing seems to be capable of unhinging your thoughts. Your Will saving throw increases by one step, to a maximum of legendary. If this causes your Will to reach master or better or it already was, treat successes with your Will saving throws as critical successes. If your class would later increase your Will save, increase your Will another step as if you had just taken this feat after factoring in the level the class puts you at, which may also get you the other effect.</p>"
